{"tid":607773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美瀕貿易戰，支那進口果販：當然幫自己人，給錢美國賺不可能！","createTime":"2018-03-27T14:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T17:59:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"64c90d27258820d4665997c13832429f256b155e","tid":607773,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰劍拔弩張，但無阻一眾進口生果商販落力叫賣。位於廣州白雲區的大型生果集散地，丁財兩旺，銷售網絡遍布全國。<br />\n<br />\n有水果商販賣的美國鮮橙，佔了一半生意，一旦爆發貿易戰，將首當其衝，目前只好努力尋找新貨源。亦有人認為做生意最重要「政治正確」：「和她（美國）打架，肯定不進口，沒有可能，對不對，始終幫助自己人，死對頭，還要給錢她賺？不可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」<br />\n<br />\n有片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1675092075968605/?fref=mentions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1675092075968605%2F%3Ffref%3Dmentions&d=Wx6tw4pFrpoXHRStRrmFkbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=90cd8897\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1675092075968605/?fref=mentions</a>"},{"pid":"21ee2f1ecc28ed52803ea8a836e635a5a83f3198","tid":607773,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚去日本啦屌你老母死蝗蟲。"},{"pid":"aa984069b80b417f61c8525ff9abac1030003fd3","tid":607773,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe68c21f3d63ce30dd92be8dabb7700a6258669","tid":607773,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉入口日本生果<br />\n抵制美帝"},{"pid":"f9b95dd34db32efb0ddbbfaf2516a5d9af23b577","tid":607773,"uid":76310,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:46:29.000Z","msg":"入美國貨=比美國賺錢<br />